right side.

Distribution/Business Practices

The automotive market in Poland is organized in a unique way.  Only sole
representatives of producers are entitled to legally import new vehicles into
Poland.  Each cooperates closely with the network of car dealers.  Each
importer supplies the dealers with imported cars.  This way of organizing the
distribution helps Polish authorities to control the distribution of
duty-free quota cars.

